          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Bankruptcy Administration Improvement Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill increases the amount of compensation paid to trustees in chapter 7 (liquidation) bankrtupcy proceedings. Similarly, it increases the statutory filing fee for bankruptcy petitions under chapter 7.</p>]]></text>
